[01:42.83] But now the days have turned to years
[02:01.33] 
[01:49.65] I was something she could use
[01:52.60] Like a good friend or a pair of shoes
[01:56.31] Or any kind of good news
[02:08.31] 
[02:07.84] Now the eastern sky is crimson and red
[02:10.30] As I lie here in my lonely bed
